      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Both front airbags deployed, but the rest of the interior looks to be in good condition, although the front-end sure doesn’t. A laminated piece of paper on the passenger seat shows the asking price of $499,000. Now the Alpina Z8 is worth a fraction of that.",
